video.title: The Day My Butt Went Psycho!
video.synopsis: A boy and his best friend -- his newly detached butt -- embark on wacky adventures in a world where humans and their butts live side by side.

episodes.synopsis: After a video of Zack and Deuce beat boxing goes viral, the Butts fire Zack; Zack resolves to capture the fierce Buttsquatch and prove his excellence.
episodes.title: Beat Box Butt / Legend of the Buttsquatch

episodes.synopsis: Gran leaves her butt behind to act as a baby sitter for Zack and Deuce; Zack sets out to perform three heroic feats to prove he's the Chosen One.
episodes.title: Grandparents’ Butts Just Don’t Understand / Comic Butt Convention

episodes.synopsis: When Eleanor scoffs at Zack's disguise, they vie to see who can sneak into the museum gala; Zack picks Eleanor to fight with in the Glutiator battle.
episodes.title: Zackster of Disguise / Glutiator

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Deuce grow moustaches, putting Deuce in a tricky position; Zack glues Eleanor and Deuce together with super sticky gum.
episodes.title: Buttstache / Journey to the Center of the Mabeltown Crack

episodes.synopsis: A robot toilet from the future tries to stop the butt who destroyed Earth, but Zack accidentally spoils its efforts; Zack becomes allergic to Deuce.

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Deuce switch bodies right before the Spanky Awards; Deuce misunderstands the point of Harmony Day, and Zack must protect him from Silas.

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Deuce convince the last remaining soldier from the Great Butt War that Butts are good; Silas's butt fighter milkshake makes Deuce a genius.

episodes.synopsis: The Great White Butt grabs Zack, Eleanor and the mysterious Dark Nugget; after Zack, Deuce and Eleanor reach the Dodgebutt finals, Deuce goes psycho.

episodes.synopsis: Zack's craving for an animal sidekick gets him a Buttasaurus with a taste for secret sauce; when the Butt Menace Meter breaks, Zack steps in.
episodes.title: Jurassic Fart / Basic In-Stink

episodes.synopsis: Deuce discovers that being king stinks, so he and Zack look for a replacement; Zack tries to find King Tush-ankhamun's missing porcelain throne.
episodes.title: Royal Flush / Game of Porcelain Thrones

episodes.synopsis: A new video game leads the town to expel Silas, leaving the Great White Butt unopposed; Zack and Deuce use their new butt buggy to race the bad butts.

episodes.synopsis: Zack removes the butts' stink, with unexpected results; the B-Team competes on a reality show, and Zack must prove that things are not as they seem.

episodes.synopsis: Zack runs errands with Gran, but never notices her secret powers; Deuce falls asleep after he and Zack win a contest and only Eleanor can wake him.
episodes.title: Gran to Gran Combat / Snoozing Booty

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Eleanor search for Deuce when the Plumber Butt takes him to the sewers; Zack and Deuce go to cheerleader camp instead of butt fighter camp.
episodes.title: The Legend of the Plumber Butt /  Butt I’m a Cheerleader

episodes.synopsis: Gran invites a glum Great White Butt to room with Zack and Deuce; all the town's power enters Deuce's body, which suits the Great White Butt's plans.
episodes.title: Everybooty Loves the Great White Butt /  Brown Out

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Deuce think they were switched at birth with rich kid Jonas and his butt; Bummy Rippa comes to town to film a movie about the Dark Nugget.
episodes.title: Switched at Butt / The Dark Nugget Returns

episodes.synopsis: By accident, Zack creates a new fashion craze that jeopardizes the town; a robo-butt takes Zack hostage, forcing Deuce and Eleanor to rescue him.

episodes.synopsis: As Deuce recovers from amnesia, he imagines he is a butt fighter; Zack and Deuce infiltrate a butts-only club and learn some butt secrets.

episodes.synopsis: When Deuce inhales a flatulence genie, he gains the power to grant wishes; after Deuce plays a banned trumpet, Butt Monkeys take over the town.

episodes.synopsis: The Prince of Pantsylvania holds the town's underwear supply hostage; when Deuce accidentally becomes a circus star, Zack pushes him to extremes.

episodes.synopsis: The Great White Butt's mom comes to visit, and terror ripples throughout the town; Deuce turns to Derriere to help him become more cultured.

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Deuce accidentally break open the fartinental divide; Eleanor is getting a new next-door neighbor: Paige the cheerleader!

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Deuce accidentally create crop circles in a field, making the town think that aliens will invade; Deuce wins a day with Silas Sterne.

episodes.synopsis: While toilet fishing, Deuce is hooked by a famed potty angler and must find his long-lost goldfish to be released; Zack forms his own fighting squad.

episodes.synopsis: The kids spend the night in the town's haunted outhouse; when Zack is named last on a list of butt fighters, he decides to scoop ice cream instead.

episodes.synopsis: When Deuce swallows Silas Sterne's secret message, the kids need a translator who can speak Fartinese; Deuce's farts create a buttnado.

episodes.synopsis: When the guys come out of the bathtub shriveled, they are mistaken for old men; Zack, Eleanor and Deuce try to track down a mystery butt fighter.
episodes.title: The Old Butts and the Sea / Pinch Me If You Can

episodes.synopsis: An accident in Zack's art class brings Deuce fame as a fartistic genius; a splash of radioactive toilet water gives Deuce a superpowered tongue.
episodes.title: Exit Through the Outhouse / Bums of Steel

episodes.synopsis: The kids form a band of smell-erasing butt fighters, but accidentally create a huge stink monster; Deuce takes Zack's place at a photo shoot.
episodes.title: Backdrafters / Calendar Butt

episodes.synopsis: The kids get lost in the Brown Forest and stumble onto Eleanor's long-lost bossy butt; when Bunbury is accidentally destroyed, Deuce must stand in.
episodes.title: Eleanor, Smellanor / Breaking Bunbury

episodes.synopsis: Zack gets a plunger stuck on his head and is mistaken for a mythical creature; a contest for butts turns into a competition among smelly humans.

episodes.synopsis: Zack goes to extremes to get his demo to 2-Ply, the world's greatest limericksologist; Zack mistakenly bows out of a cheerleading competition.

episodes.synopsis: Zack becomes the spokesmodel for a new butt fighter cereal; Deuce lands the lead role in "Hambutt," the long-lost play from Shakespeare's butt.

episodes.synopsis: The gang has to help Eleanor after a walk in the Brown Forest leaves her stinky; when Bummy Rippa comes to town, Zack is chosen as his ambassador.

episodes.synopsis: Deuce has lost his brain, and the guys only have a few hours to find it; Zack's aptitude test results say that he is destined to be a bad guy.

episodes.synopsis: A film inspires Zack to help ordinary citizens become heroes; when Zack is accused of ruining a ritual event, he must prove he is a friend to butts.

episodes.synopsis: When Zack and Deuce's house becomes its own country, a game of dodgebutt must settle their power struggle; the doctor tells Deuce he is out of farts.

episodes.synopsis: Zack tricks out Gran's toilet, and everyone wants him to build custom bowls for them; the kids and Robutts form a temporary alliance.
episodes.title: F2: Flushment Day / The Great White Buff

episodes.synopsis: Deuce finds he can play a new sport and teams up with a strange janitor who has big plans for him; Zack and Eleanor play a banned game of Silas Says.
episodes.title: Jani-Thor / Silas Says

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Deuce go into space and mistakenly release the world's most evil butt; a rearranging machine replaces everyone's heads with their butts.
episodes.title: Bring Me the Butt of Silas Sterne - Part I / Bring Me the Butt of Silas Sterne - Part 2
